    <fr:title text="Noetherian topological spaces">Noetherian topological spaces</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>
  A topoloigcal space <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex> is <html:em>Noetherian</html:em> if it has no infinite strictly decreasing closed spaces.
</html:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
